latestPosts.caption:
My dream bag from Goyard🥰 The Saïgon Structuré Nano bag from 2024 in the limited edition color Pearly Blue💙💙💙🦋 My hopes of getting this bag was not high actually… The Saïgon Structuré bag is a true iconic bag and rather hard to get and chances to get it in the Nano size is like almost nonexistent😅 But our sweet SA always knew that I wanted it in the Nano size for years and he totally surprised me with this one🥹🙏🏻It‘s so precious and I‘m feeling like Arielle the mermaid wearing it🥰🤪 As this surprise wasn’t enough… The St. Louis tote in Pearly Green also came home with me🙏🏻
